      • sum

        public static <T extends java.lang.Number & java.lang.Comparable> T sum(java.util.Collection<T> values)
        Returns the sum of the passed Numbers (which are CovTerm values), skipping null values. Used for BigDecimal and Integer types only, as these are the only underlying datatypes for Numeric covterms.
        Parameters:
        values - a collection of Numbers to be summed
        Returns:
        the sum of the passed values; the type of the returned value is that of the passed values
